quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  39,75,"Uzabona kandi abamalayika bakikije Ar’shi, basingiza ikuzo n’ishimwe bya Nyagasani wabo. Kandi (ibiremwa byose) bizakiranurwa mu kuri. Nuko havugwe ngo “Ishimwe n’ikuzo byuzuye ni ibya Allah, Nyagasani w’ibiremwa byose.”"
  40,1,Haa Miimu
  40,2,"Ihishurwa ry’igitabo (Qur’an) rituruka kuri Allah, Umunyacyubahiro bihebuje, Umumenyi uhebuje"
  40,3,"Ubabarira ibyaha, Uwakira ukwicuza, Nyiribihano bikaze, Nyirinema. Nta yindi mana ibaho itari We, kandi Iwe ni ho garukiro"
  40,4,"Nta bajya impaka ku bimenyetso bya Allah, usibye ba bandi bahakanye. Bityo, ntugashukwe no kwidegembya kwabo ku isi"
  40,5,"Mbere yabo (Abakurayishi), n’abantu ba Nuhu ndetse n’udutsiko twaje nyuma yabo barahakanye. Kandi buri muryango w’abantu washakaga kwica intumwa yawutumweho, ndetse bajya impaka zishingiye ku kinyoma bagamije kuburizamo ukuri, maze ndabafata (ndabahana). Mbega uko ibihano byanjye byari bimeze"
  40,6,"Ndetse uko ni ko ijambo rya Nyagasani wawe (ry’ibihano) ryabaye impamo kuri ba bandi bahakanye, ko rwose ari abantu bo mu muriro"
  40,7,"Ba bandi (abamalayika) bateruye Ar’shi n’abayikikije, basingiza ikuzo rya Nyagasani wabo bakanamwemera, bakanasabira imbabazi ba bandi bemera (bagira bati) “Nyagasani wacu! Impuhwe n’ubumenyi byawe bigera kuri buri kintu. None babarira ibyaha ba bandi bakwicujijeho, bakanakurikira inzira yawe ndetse unabarinde ibihano byo mu muriro.”"